abstract: New York Jets coach Rex Ryan comments on team's victory over Miami Dolphins, presumably the worst team in the league, while Jets prepare for upcoming game against San Diego Chargers.
snippet: The Jets did several things well against Miami, but they face tougher teams in San Diego, Buffalo and New England in the coming weeks.
lead_paragraph: The Jets did several things well against Miami, but they face tougher teams in San Diego, Buffalo and New England in the coming weeks.

headline.main: Despite Victory, Concerns About Jets Remain
